<lb ed="I" n="0078b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0078b0101">大魏永安三年歲次庚戌七月甲戌十一日□
<lb ed="I" n="0078b02" type="honorific"/>夫大聖慈隆。演化脩導。善業顯彰。倉生咸慕。曠代遵
<lb ed="I" n="0078b03" type="honorific"/>崇。<note n="0078001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30560"/>＝虛【史】</note><note n="0078001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30560"/>【佛拓】，虛【史】</note><app n="0078001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虛</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30560"/></rdg></app>空无碍。雖<note n="0078002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30561"/>＝冥【史】</note><note n="0078002" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30561"/>【佛拓】，冥【史】</note><app n="0078002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">冥</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30561"/></rdg></app>運不弔。真容凝位。是故
<lb ed="I" n="0078b04" type="honorific"/>釋□□生。以<note n="0078003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">啔＝啓【史】</note><note n="0078003" resp="ihp" type="mod">啔【佛拓】，啓【史】</note><app n="0078003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">啓</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">啔</rdg></app><note n="0078004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30562"/>＝權【史】</note><note n="0078004" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30562"/>【佛拓】，權【史】</note><app n="0078004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">權</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30562"/></rdg></app>曜。是以形教之興。敷沾有氣之
<lb ed="I" n="0078b05" type="honorific"/>□□□影念貌遺像。但雙等。規奉玄門。幼染繢服。
<lb ed="I" n="0078b06" type="honorific"/>□□□巖岳寄氣。松石自慨。剾□返掌蹉跌又□
<lb ed="I" n="0078b07" type="honorific"/>□□□命如朝露。<note n="0078005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30563"/>＝仰【史】</note><note n="0078005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30563"/>【佛拓】，仰【史】</note><app n="0078005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">仰</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30563"/></rdg></app><note n="0078006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30564"/>＝勸【史】</note><note n="0078006" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30564"/>【佛拓】，勸【史】</note><app n="0078006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">勸</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30564"/></rdg></app>師僧同<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">學</unclear>　衣鉢
<lb ed="I" n="0078b08" type="honorific"/>□□□四背。減妻子之珍。分於末代□
<lb ed="I" n="0078b09" type="honorific"/>□□餘人。咸自開悟。建　釋迦石像
<lb ed="I" n="0078b10" type="honorific"/>□□薩兩師子。并天宮一區。起永安□
<lb ed="I" n="0078b11" type="honorific"/>功□□月十一日營訖。妙體沖邃。容貌澄相
<lb ed="I" n="0078b12" type="honorific"/>光曜　<note n="0078007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30565"/>＝邊【史】</note><note n="0078007" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30565"/>【佛拓】，邊【史】</note><app n="0078007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邊</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30565"/></rdg></app>外。<app type="star" corresp="#0078005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">仰</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30563"/></rdg></app>為
<lb ed="I" n="0078b13" type="honorific"/>皇帝　陛下。群遼百<note n="0078008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30566"/>＝辟【史】</note><note n="0078008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30566"/>【佛拓】，辟【史】</note><app n="0078008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">辟</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30566"/></rdg></app>。中宮內外。師僧父母。因緣眷
<lb ed="I" n="0078b14" type="honorific"/>屬。善<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">友</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">知</unclear>識。<note n="0078009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30567"/>＝逮【史】</note><note n="0078009" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30567"/>【佛拓】，逮【史】</note><app n="0078009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">逮</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30567"/></rdg></app>及七世。一切无<app type="star" corresp="#0078007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邊</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30565"/></rdg></app>眾生。願沾　　速
<lb ed="I" n="0078b15" type="honorific"/>成正覺。□同斯福　　大像邑都唯那比丘道陰
<lb ed="I" n="0078b16" type="honorific"/>□□□大像邑主前廣業寺主比丘慧雙<note n="0078010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30568"/>＝率【史】</note><note n="0078010" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30568"/>【佛拓】，率【史】</note><app n="0078010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">率</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30568"/></rdg></app>造
<lb ed="I" n="0078b17" type="honorific"/>□□□□</p>
